[Course_Description]
Learn how to find video production jobs and get paid to make commercials for brands and businesses. Instructor Garret Johnson is a professional freelance director who has created videos for numerous high-profile clients. In this course, he explains how to create amazing commercials that build your portfolio and grow your client list. Learn how to reach out to new clients, build pitches, and develop your demo reel. Find out how to get the job done by acquiring the right equipment and running a professional set. Finally, learn how to deliver the job, handle revisions, and use your current work as the springboard to your next job. This course was created by CreatorUp. We are pleased to host this content in our library.